Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What miracle is going to happen \Nunder the moonlight tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... So you know the owner, Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like his name should be "Terai," \Nbut it's pronounced "Jii." Weird, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call him Jii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Saturday afternoon \Nand the place is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii-chan! Coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna serve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:00.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, getting me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean this coffee's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worse than me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a hustler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "magician"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never beaten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You been yakkety-yakkin' since comin' in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brats shouldn't be shootin' \Npool to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a place to hit balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a place to hit people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hit somebody, do it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You won't be givin' me \Nthe high hat much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is deserted with all your \Ncustomers flockin' to the boss's pool bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss has the Legendary Cue \Nat his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why nobody's comin' \Nto your hole in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I come, it'll be to \Nbuy this place from you dirt cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But what was he saying \Nabout some "Legendary Cue"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Cue is inlaid with \Ncountless diamonds and emeralds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's said that only \Na champion can wield it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamonds and emeralds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:27.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about the place that has that cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pool hall called American \Nin front of the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you have to be 18 or over\N and dressed up to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Billiards should be fun to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Age and clothes have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'd like to get a look \Nat an awesome cue like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you have it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:59.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I played a game of pool, \Nwith that cue as the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I met your father, Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.27,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Hustler vs. Magician
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:15.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I used to rake \Nit in as a pool shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pool shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, pool is an \Nenjoyable pastime for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but back in the day, it was \Nall about the gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a lone wolf who never lost, but \Nsome people didn't take kindly to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasura Tsujiro worked for the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a sharp hustler \Nat the top of his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:51.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made just one error.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From that point on, \NHasura had control of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I never got another turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were an expert, right, Jii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you have blown it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeknownst even to Hasura,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the syndicate boss doctored my chalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't object?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice it then, and I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Hasura really was talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done a lot for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll get that Legendary Cue back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsujiro, come here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got somethin' interesting to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}To Hasura-sama: \NI'm going to take \Nthe Legendary Cue \Nat 10:00 tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, should we call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! They're already keeping \Nan eye on us these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd ask them for even more attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Aoko is always late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of outfit is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a middle school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Presto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you gotta wear something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You touched my butt back there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have to act like a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How else was I supposed to dress you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you did touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two really college students?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! We're married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate ice cream. Make it a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll know you're still a kid \Nif you order stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! What can I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a chocolate parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about ordering an adult-like cocktail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocktail? With alcohol? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Martini, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip the alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. But maybe she at least \Nlooks like she belongs here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's that Hasura guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Hasura-sama is \Nplaying in the secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir, but there's a 50,000 yen charge \Njust for being a spectator in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with {\i1}Weekly Magic Sunday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we want to publish an article in next \Nweek's issue, called "Just Like a Magician!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Cool Techniques of a Brilliant Hustler."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for an article?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine ball in the corner pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely Tsujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? That was a lousy shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna make the Legendary \NCue cry with skill like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii, huh? He comes in here \Nafter all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just supposed to observe tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from a magazine, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you play against Tsujiro once?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm game!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Jii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsujiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii, is he a hustler?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:21.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One game, 10,000 yen. \NLet's go with nine ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know straight pool, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, you're at a disadvantage \Nif you don't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jii-chan! It's still just a \Nmatter of knocking the balls in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except in straight ball, \Nyou can target any of the balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,whereas with nine ball, \Nyou have to sink them in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you brilliantly knock in the \Neight ball, miss nine and you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:12:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you knock the nine ball in \Nduring the opening break, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, it sounds easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did know that sinking the cue ball
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is a foul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unlucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasura-sama is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...nine ball is a game of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And drawing the luck to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a type of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! He doesn't only have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got guts that attract luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. This is a match \Nbetween an adult and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna quit while you're behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsujiro won this set, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 100,000 in losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, I can't afford...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's raise the stakes. We'll put the \NBlue Parrot pool hall on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for your side, \Nyou put up the Legendary Cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young Master! How am I supposed to \Nmake a living if I lose my place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! What's a business or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is Kid the Phantom Thief's headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play, knowing that I would \Ntake away Jii's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it. We can make good money \Nwith that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it. Your job is to hit \Nthe balls in like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not askin' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order, Tsujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He accepts the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a tool to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, a showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jii, but I'm gonna win this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink the one, then a two-nine \Ncombination to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! I'm here to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A nuisance got in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The balls are fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you playing this slow crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito can't win with music like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, something that Kaito likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now we're talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Lady Luck's on my side now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's having so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I enjoy myself like that \Nduring matches these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cut the noise when it's his turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have him getting distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Billiards is a game you play for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, as for his turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't gonna get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even sink the easy shots, so \Nthere's no way you can handle this setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that position...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Toichi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:06.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, who do you think is the \Nmost important person in a circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The person on the flying trapeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clowns are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clowns are lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, to satisfy the audience, \Nthey have to fail deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:27.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even more difficult than succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But clowns have to laugh the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's to catch the audience off guard \Nand heighten their amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's their poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cue ball made two jumps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gettin' that cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You said you'd give it if I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, adults are liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And lying is the first step \Nto becoming a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning the secret, you have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like the flavor \Nof my paralyzing powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! You can't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, I'm absconding \Nwith the Legendary Cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Your advance notice is nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your note said you were going \Nto steal the cue from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but now it belongs to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That cue can only belong to a true champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been protecting it for 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and now I want to give it to that \Nyoung man with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm embarrassed for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting outside the bounds of my advance notice \Nwould bring shame to my good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Organized Crime Task Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody move! You're under \Narrest for gun smuggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with us down \Nto the station voluntarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. I was just lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There are two Kaitos?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you can use magic \Nto manipulate luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what happens, \Na showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't mind, I'd like to \Nplay against you again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Jii-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Young Master works \Nthis old man too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.64,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were \Na hustler, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I told you that was just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never beat me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You relied on luck with my business at stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference? I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm not a hustler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a lucky streak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between a hustler and a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it luck or the poker face \Nof a clown that won the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:33.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm devoting myself to stealing as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when an arrogant guy just back \Nfrom England appears before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Detectives are a phantom thief's rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't met one yet \Nwho's a match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you wanna show me what you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NA Great Detective Comes to Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:52.74,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,A Great Detective Comes to Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:55.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
